<sect2>
<title>Installation of Shadow Password Suite</title>

<para>Install the Shadow Password Suite by running the following commands:</para>

<para><screen><userinput>patch -Np1 -i ../shadow-20001016.patch &amp;&amp;</userinput>
<userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;</userinput>
<userinput>make &amp;&amp;</userinput>
<userinput>make install &amp;&amp;</userinput>
<userinput>cd etc &amp;&amp;</userinput>
<userinput>cp limits login.access /etc &amp;&amp;</userinput>
<userinput>sed "s|/var/spool/mail|/var/mail|" login.defs.linux &gt; /etc/login.defs</userinput></screen></para>

</sect2>

